{"tid":1002294,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚引玉］一人一個扑野被人撞破既經歷","createTime":"2019-01-30T23:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T05:21:39.000Z","uid":42927,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a784f8a485364d6071f48cd36e4b7b560414edb6","tid":1002294,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T23:36:02.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n小弟係最後一屆AL ge考生<br />\n考試咁梗係要溫書架啦<br />\n溫書梗係要係屋企溫先溫到啦<br />\n咁係條女屋企溫書就更加事半功倍 （E家已經係ex ）<br />\n<br />\n我帶齊書同埋dom，興致勃勃咁去ex屋企。<br />\n上到當然有溫書啦，咁溫到肚餓就煮野食啦<br />\nex叫我煮腸仔蛋面，但係咁啱雪櫃無曬腸，咁ex就食我個條啦<br />\n正當我地係房度激戰時，ex又好大聲，<br />\n&rdquo;叮噹&rdquo;<br />\n我地即刻著翻衫，我拎曬所有野企係房門後。<br />\nex去o左開門，係uncle黎。<br />\n點知uncle入o廁所去大<br />\n我007上身，用忍者般o既步法跳出屋企門口<br />\n就咁避過一劫<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴絲又有乜經歷呢"},{"pid":"e1769731d4a4270948a149747157345a0205e246","tid":1002294,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T23:37:59.000Z","msg":"扑到一半blue ball 住走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68efc2e1a872e80d4959b647a1ea8240907150c8","tid":1002294,"uid":83808,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T23:38:26.000Z","msg":"uncle番自己屋企都㩒鐘<br />\n都算比面"},{"pid":"506d7375569fb6a3045935cbfad007d9b3842f79","tid":1002294,"uid":17747,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"68efc2e1a872e80d4959b647a1ea8240907150c8","tid":1002294,"uid":83808,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T23:38:26.000Z","msg":"uncle番自己屋企都㩒鐘<br />\n都算比面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T23:39:37.000Z","msg":"佢都後生過"},{"pid":"a51e7a4a556236198a0b584aad3756213195ea2c","tid":1002294,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1769731d4a4270948a149747157345a0205e246","tid":1002294,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T23:37:59.000Z","msg":"扑到一半blue ball 住走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T23:41:33.00